title: IDM.UltraEdit.v22.0.0.46.Incl.Keymaker-CORE

UltraEdit is the ideal text, HTML and HEX editor, and an advanced PHP, Perl, Java and JavaScript editor for programmers. An industry-award winner, UltraEdit supports disk-based 64-bit file handling (standard) on 32-bit Windows platforms (Windows 2000 and later).

iNSTALL/REGiSTER NOTES
==================
1. Extract with 7-Zip.
2. Install the application.
3. Patch the hosts file manually.
- Add the following lines to your hosts file in WINDOWSsystem32driversetc:
127.0.0.1 licensing.ultraedit.com
127.0.0.1 licensing2.ultraedit.com
4. In menu Help, use activate / offline-activation.
5. Enter anything for license ID and password.
6. Now use our keygen to activate the software
